programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Taste of France S1 - "Pascal Barbot - Astrance"
programme.desc: In today’s program we will visit the star-chef Pascal Barbot, who became independent at age twenty-seven. Reservations at his 2 star Michelin-awarded restaurant Astrance are booked months ahead.

programme.title: Daniel Barratier – L’Auberge Sur-les-Bois
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Taste of France S1 - "Daniel Barratier – L’Auberge Sur-les-Bois"
programme.desc: Daniel Barratier has worked with some of the best chefs traveling the world, now he’s back in his hometown, Annecy, the ”Venice of the French Alps" were he invested in a true fine dining restaurant.

programme.title: Philippines: Why is Filipino food unpopular?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Philippines: Why is Filipino food unpopular?"
programme.desc: Liesel embarks on a journey to the country of over 7000 islands, the Philippines. From the serene to the seedy, she combs through metro Manila discovering the food; this culinary spectrum includes bouncing around trying the popular fast food joints, meeting the local experts such as blogger Cheryl Tiu, a taste of history at the worlds oldest Chinatown, an unexpected dancing session at the Spanish haunts of Manila, to rubbing shoulders with the elite Chefs of the city. All in a quest to answer just why Filipino cuisine is unheard of!

programme.title: Thailand: US Thai Food vs Authentic-Thai, which is the winner?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Thailand: US Thai Food vs Authentic-Thai, which is the winner?"
programme.desc: Liesel embarks on a journey to the country of over 7000 islands, the Philippines. From the serene to the seedy, she combs through metro Manila discovering the food; this culinary spectrum includes bouncing around trying the popular fast food joints, meeting the local experts such as blogger Cheryl Tiu, a taste of history at the worlds oldest Chinatown, an unexpected dancing session at the Spanish haunts of Manila, to rubbing shoulders with the elite Chefs of the city. All in a quest to answer just why Filipino cuisine is unheard of!

programme.title: India: Can Kolkata be considered a foodie destination of India?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Maximum Foodie S1 - "India: Can Kolkata be considered a foodie destination of India?"
programme.desc: Liesel pinballs around a city known for its gastronomy, the forgotten hub of British East India trading company, Kolkata. From trying out what the bustling city’s vibrant street food scene has to offer, to the lesser known gems, including, venturing into India’s only Chinatown and sampling their delicacies. A tale of walking food tours, hole in the wall joints serving up North Eastern dumplings, messy fish markets, and of course, the pride of Bengal, the Hilsa fish. Is Kolkata up to par with the other major metropolitan cities of India? This episode finds out exactly that!

programme.title: Nevada: What else is there in Nevada for foodies besides Vegas?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Nevada: What else is there in Nevada for foodies besides Vegas?"
programme.desc: This investigative mission starts off in the sin city atmosphere of the Vegas strip. After a gluttonous stint at a generic buffet, Liesel is inspired to do a road trip to find iconic gems in the state of Nevada. From ghost towns, to monstrous foodie challenges, to hole in the wall dive bars in the middle of nowhere, this trip has it all. Liesel finds the resurgence of Basque cuisine in Northern Nevada, and learns that Reno can do fine dining as well! A trip to Virginia city also reveals that the Silver State has some haunted bars where patrons from the 1800s are rumored to be still imbibing and spooking locals! It’s a road trip in every sense of the word!

programme.title: Rome: What are the tourists missing out on?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Rome: What are the tourists missing out on?"
programme.desc: Italy is a vacationer’s paradise. The food, the people, the sights and sounds, the history! But are the tourists doing it right when it comes to the trying out authentic food in Rome? Liesel embarks on a mission to explore the street food of the city. With the help of her food journalist buddy, Saverio de Luca, Liesel sifts through pasticceri, food festivals, touristed hotspots, all in an effort to understand real Roman food.

programme.title: Emlia Romagna: What’s the food like?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Emlia Romagna: What’s the food like?"
programme.desc: The region of Emilia Romagna is lush with gentle rolling hills where time honored ingredients like truffles, olives, and vast vineyards can be found. But this region is usually overshadowed by it’s more famous neighboring cities, Florence and Venice. To understand the food of this region, Liesel explores the quaint sea-side town of Rimini and the hugely impressive Bologna. Its a tale of discovering local foodie passion that allows Liesel to hunt for truffles and try her hand in making her own gelato, a the world’s only Gelato University!

programme.title: Mexico: Tequila: Does it need to come from certain regions of Mexico?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Mexico: Tequila: Does it need to come from certain regions of Mexico?"
programme.desc: In the land of tequila, Liesel gets the skinny on the premium export of Jalisco, blue agave tequila. From harvesting agave with the legendary jimadores, to understanding the process of distillation, Liesel is on the hunt to appreciate and understand the production requirements of this spirit that makes it what it is. Are they worth it only if they’re from Jalisco or can they be made somewhere else for cheaper and better..? Liesel finds out!

programme.title: Los Angeles: Food trucks: are they any good?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Los Angeles: Food trucks: are they any good?"
programme.desc: It’s a well known fact that Los Angeles is the trendsetter for entertainment, fashion, and outlandish celebrity exploits. But is it the same story with the food? Liesel explores the food truck bubble to figure out what started the craze, why its so popular, and more importantly, is the food any good?

programme.title: Indonesia - Balinese cuisine: what is it all about?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Indonesia - Balinese cuisine: what is it all about?"
programme.desc: Balinese cuisine is considered to be extremely complex. Different than what you find in the rest of Indonesia, Bali is further influenced by the major influx of Western tourism. Have the locals kept their traditions and cooking methods strong against the wave of tourism, or have they been catered to suit the palates of foreigners? Liesel heads to the ultimate getaway paradise island, sifts through all the yoga retreats, surfer shacks, and coffee plantations all in an effort to find iconic food - as well as track down the current foodie trend of the island.

programme.title: Ireland - Dublin, what else is there besides the pub culture
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Ireland - Dublin, what else is there besides the pub culture"
programme.desc: Admit it, first thing you relate with Dublin are the pubs. Sure, they are a staple and they serve some of the best brews in the world. And they come with an associated culture that is hard to rival. But what about the food? Does Dublin have a burgeoning foodie scene or is it all about the pint o’ Guiness? Find out on this episode of Max Foodie as Liesel explores the breathtakingly beautiful country of Ireland.

programme.title: A Twist on the Classic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Streetfood Nomad: Kolkata S1 - "A Twist on the Classic"
programme.desc: In the northeast of India in the state of West Benghal, Kolkata lies on the banks of the Ganges River and is a melting pot of cultures and cuisines. Inspired by Kolkatas heritage, Will puts his own twist on classic Indian dishes, reinventing and infusing these recipes with unexpected flavours.

programme.title: Eastern Port
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Streetfood Nomad: Kolkata S1 - "Eastern Port"
programme.desc: The Eastern port Kolkata has been the centre for international merchants and migrants. The closest entry-point from China, in 1778 Kolkota became home to India’s only Chinese community. They have left an indelible mark on Kolkata’s architecture, culture and cuisine.

programme.title: The Street Scene
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Streetfood Nomad: Kolkata S1 - "The Street Scene"
programme.desc: Kolkata’s extraordinary street-food scene has been influenced by its various conquerors and rulers. The most profound influence has been from the fabulously rich and powerful Mughals. Will reimagines classic dishes while also incorporating the unique street food flavours he encounters.

programme.title: Fuelling the Workforce
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Streetfood Nomad: Kolkata S1 - "Fuelling the Workforce"
programme.desc: The city of Kolkata is one of the most densely populated in the world. That’s a lot of mouths to feed. Fortunately, it’s a place that knows just how to do it. Fuelled by the bustling energy of street vendors, Will seeks inspiration from Indian working mans essentials.

programme.title: Belize
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 The Delinquent Gourmet S1 - "Belize"
programme.desc: Gord is in Dangriga, Belize to explore the countrys unique melting pot of African, Spanish and Caribbean cuisines. Taking to the streets, he tastes the wares of vendor after vendor - Johnnycakes, tamales, garnaches - Belizes heavenly taco. And then at the Dangriga market, our Delinquent Gourmet discovers varieties of fish hes never even heard of!

programme.title: Portugal
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 The Delinquent Gourmet S1 - "Portugal"
programme.desc: Rodney is in Porto, Portugal. And although hes not yet a huge fan of Portuguese food, hes here to see if this seaside city can inspire him to change his mind. After watching the fishermen haul in their catch, Rodney cooks up lunch for one of the fishermen and his wife.

programme.title: Fez, Morocco
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 The Delinquent Gourmet S1 - "Fez, Morocco"
programme.desc: In Fez, Morocco, not much has changed since the Middle Ages but Rodney is determined to stir things up and find tantalizing new dishes he can bring home.

programme.title: Sardinia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 The Delinquent Gourmet S1 - "Sardinia"
programme.desc: Rodney is in Sardinia, Italy, where he finds culinary inspiration around every corner. High in the Sardinian hills, his hosts prepare their specialty - roasted suckling pig. After sitting down to an outdoor family meal (where even the dog helps himself!), Rodney samples a myrtle-flavored liquor before dancing with his gentlemen hosts.

programme.title: The Original Fast Food
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Streetfood Nomad: Kolkata S1 - "The Original Fast Food"
programme.desc: In a vibrant exploration of textures and tastes, Will dives into the world of Indian street food chats and snacks, some of the most loved and sought after dishes in all of India. The original fast food.

programme.title: Coffee Break
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Streetfood Nomad: Kolkata S1 - "Coffee Break"
programme.desc: In Kolkata street-food isn’t only about the Hawker stalls. The Coffee Houses are part meeting place, part restaurant, part community hall. Serving up quick and simple food for the multitudes.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Khanh Ongs Wild Food S1 - "Cairns, QLD"
programme.desc: Chef Khanh Ong travels to Cairns, Australia where he embarks on an adventure to the rainforests of Mission Beach. Learning from locals, he learns how to hunt mud crabs with a spear on the traditional fishing grounds of the Kuku Yalanji people.

Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: Jesse James Rides Again
programme.desc: The outlaw Jesse James and his friend are on the run from the law when he is wrongly accused of leading the historic 1876 Northfield, Minnesota bank robbery. With nerve-tensing turns and high-impact action, Jesse rides into a town where a gang is trying to drive area ranchers off their land because theres oil underneath it. Jesse James takes particular interest in the situation of a pretty young woman and her elderly father, whose ranch is being regularly attacked by the gang.

programme.title: The Star Packer
programme.desc: He Dared Death In The Outlaws Lair! John Travers (John Wayne) takes on a mysterious gang leader known as The Shadow in this vintage western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Director/writer Robert N. Bradbury (Blue Steel, Riders of Destiny) gets the best of a remarkable cast that includes George Gabby Hayes. Of interest to film buffs is that the feature was shot in various California locations by Oscar winning cinematographer Archie Stout (The Quiet Man).

programme.title: Raiders of Red Gap
programme.desc: Bobs Playin A Mystery Hand... Hes Marked For Death By Killer Bullets As Gunfire Echoes Over The Plains! After one of his ranch hands is killed when a gang attacks his ranch, Jim Roberts joins forces with his neighbor in an effort to fight off the Bennett Cattle Co., a company looking to rob them of their land. Things get increasingly dangerous as the company hires Butch Crane, a professional killer, to stop them. Directed by Sam Newfield (Racing Luck (1935), Go-Get-Em, Haines (1936)), Raiders of Red Gap stars Robert Livingston (The Three Mesquiteers (1936), Larceny on the Air (1937)) as Rocky (Lone Rider) Cameron and Al St. John (Billy the Kid Trapped (1942), Border Feud (1947)) as...

programme.title: The Sundowners
programme.desc: Brother battles brother in this gritty tale of feuding ranchers in the old west. This story of the Texas panhandle stars such familiar faces as Robert Preston, Chill Wills, and Jack Elam, and was a rare film for its time in that it was filmed almost entirely in Texas with no studio interiors. If for no other reason, watch this one for Prestons performance. If you only know him from The Music Man or Victor Victoria, youre sure to be surprised here! (also, look for John Drew Barrymore as Jef Cloud. He was part of the famous Barrymore family, and father of Drew Barrymore.) Jim Strake: Frank Cordell. The Whip: Dave Kashner. Directed by George Templeton

programme.title: Courageous Avenger
programme.desc: Gold, gangs, and the heroic fight for life! Johnny Mack Brown (Billy the Kid, Coquette) stars in this western thriller about murders going on in a mining community. Its a story full of twists, where the greed for gold is only surpassed by the struggle for life!

programme.title: Born to Battle
programme.desc: Cyclone Tom Saunders starts a ruckus in a Chinese laundry and has to go before a judge. Unable to pay his fine, he is bailed out by a local cattle rancher and agrees to do 30 days work for him. Its not too long before he becomes enmeshed in a war between rustlers and outlaws.

programme.title: Brothers of the West
programme.desc: Tom Tyler plays Tom Wade, a range detective whose brother has been accused of robbery and murder. Wade has only one clue to prove his brothers innocence: a set of unusual tire tracks. This film was directed by Sam Katzman, who later became known as Jungle Sam for his association with a variety of jungle thrillers, and then as a master of all exploitation genres, from teen horror to flying saucer flicks!

programme.title: Sitting Bull
programme.desc: A cavalry officer sympathetic to the wronged Sioux tribe fixes a meeting between Chief Sitting Bull and President Grant but a dishonest Indian Agent and a hateful General Custer test the Siouxs patience, threatening to derail the peace-talks. Directed and co-written by Sidney Salkow; starring Dale Robertson, Mary Murphy, J. Carrol Naish. Also, look for legendary character actor Iron Eyes Cody as Crazy Horse.

programme.title: Neath Canadian Skies
programme.desc: Its the mounties versus claim jumpers in this drama from Golden Gate Pictures. Based on an action-packed novel by James Oliver Curwood and directed by B. Reeves Maynard (Undersea Kingdom, The Phantom Empire), the film features an outstanding cast of Poverty Row regulars, including Russell Hayden, Inez Cooper, Cliff Nazarro, I. Stanford Jolley, and Kermit Maynard. For movie buffs: Cinematographer Marcel Le Picard began his career in the silent era and finished with exactly 200 credits!

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In this episode, the G-Men are sent to the Ozarks to track down gold stolen from the U.S. Government. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: An outlaw gang is stealing gold from Chinese placer miners, then driving off their claims with outrageous taxes. Because theyre Chinese, they cant sue the local government agents. With Stoney posing as a Chinese miner and Pat pretending to be a representative of an Eastern engineering company, the U.S. government tries to bring an end to the careers of the outlaw gang and crooked state government agents.

Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Episode first aired in 1963.

This episode aired in 1950.

programme.desc: Matt and Frankie arrivein the California gold fields where Frankie is kidnapped by the infamous bandit Joaquin Murietta. Without his usualy partner, Matt enlists the help of Captain Harry Love. Starring Jim Davis, Mary Castle, and Robert Anderson. Look for Rick Jason as Murietta. Jason would later go on to star in the popular ABC war series Combat!

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Following the murder of a railroad agent, Matt and Frankie work to bring the vengeful Tiburcio Vasquez to justice. Starring Jim Davis, mary Castle,Anthony Caruso, Edward Colmas, Lillian Molieri, and Eddie Parker. Also, look for Glenn Strange as Sheriff Billy Rowland. Strange was known for playing Frankensteins monster in several Universal pictures, as well as a recurring role on Gunsmoke. Also, Eddie Parker, who plays a trapper in this episode, was one of Hollywoods most revered stuntmen. Directed by William Witney. Epsiode oringinally aired in 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. In this episode, the Judge and Jeff take on the richest man in the valley over water rights. Though the rich villain has ensnared young Hugh in outlaw ways, the lawmen are determined to set Hugh on a better path. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. In this episode, Jeff Taggerts brother is accused of robbing the Del Rio bank. While investigating the case, Jeff is implicated in the hold up. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S03 : E23 The Saga of Clement O Toole
programme.desc: Mistaken for a notorious outlaw, a young man struggles to convince the townspeople that he didnt commit a stagecoach robbery. Initially, Annie and Susan Meriwether believe him, but his innocence comes into question when he is present during a bank robbery in which the outlaws seem to recognize him. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: With the sheriff off looking for an outlaw, a fake sheriff takes his place, leading to a senseless murder. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This enetertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye becomes embroiled in a fortune hunters search for treasure. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild.Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook are assigned to escort an accused criminal to his hanging.Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: After shooting Luke Grayson in self-defense, Ben Cartwright must protect himself from Graysons son, Todd, who seeks to avenge his fathers death.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC.

programme.title: Crashing Thru
programme.desc: Down the danger trail sweeps a crimson fury... as Renfrew rides again! In this action-packed adventure, Sgt. Renfrew must face off against a group of criminals involved in a gold robbery. With his partner, Constable Kelly, wounded in a gunfight, Renfrew must stop the thieves on his own. Directed by Elmer Clifton; starring James Newill and Warren Hull, this is one adventure you wont want to miss!

programme.title: Days of Jesse James
programme.desc: Famed American western actor and singer Roy Rogers once again plays himself in this Jesse James tale thats a twist on the familiar formula. When he is summoned to bring Jesse to justice after the known villain is suspected of a bank robbery, Rogers soon discovers that Jesse has been framed and that the owner of the bank has robbed his own bank posing as Jesse. Fast-paced and fun, this classic Roy Rogers western directed by Joseph Kane (Dakota) features a whole host of original songs sung by the great Rogers himself.

programme.title: Hands Across The Border
programme.desc: Roy Rogers and Trigger star in this Republic Pictures western about horse breeders vying for a contract with the U.S. Army. The cast also includes such favorites as Onslow Stevens and Guinn Big Boy Williams, while songs include Hey Hey (Its a Great Day), Dreaming to Music, and The Girl with the High Button Shoes. For movie buffs: The music for the title song, Hands Across the Border, was composed by none other than Hoagy Carmichael!

programme.title: Daniel Boone, Trailblazer
programme.desc: Daniel Boone (Bruce Bennett) battles Shawnee warriors as he leads a band of settlers into Kentucky in this frontier potboiler from Albert C. Gannaway Productions. Made at the height of Hollywoods fascination with pioneer days, the film also stars Lon Chaney Jr. as Chief Blackfish, and country singer Faron Young as a handsome young suitor for Boones daughter. Theres plenty of action and danger here as the Shawnee are convinced that Boone is trying to steal their land. But Boone is ready, not even fearing death by tomahawk. It isnt how you die, Boone says. Its what you live for.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: During the French and Indian War, Alice and Cora Munro are joined by Magua in the search for their father, a British officer. Little do they know, their father is being held captive by the Huron warriors, and Magua intends to betray them. Uncas, the last surviving warrior of the Mohican tribe and Hawkeye set out to rescue the hostages and the sisters before its too late.

programme.title: The Dawn Rider
programme.desc: John Wayne was still a few years from major stardom when he appeared as John Mason, a man seeking revenge for his fathers murder. Marion Burns stars as Alice, Masons love interest, while Reed Howes stars as Masons friend and rival for Alices affection. When Mason finally tracks down the man responsible for his fathers death, will Ben help, or stand in his way? Produced by Lone Star Pictures, the group behind many of Waynes early films, The Dawn Rider is a stirring yarn about the price of vengeance.

programme.title: One-Eyed Jacks
programme.desc: Dad Longworth robs a Mexican bank, takes the loot, and leaves his partner Rio to be captured. However, Rio escapes capture and searches for Dad in California.

programme.title: The Light of Western Stars
programme.desc: Knights of the sage-brush roar across the plains in this western drama from Harry Sherman Productions. Victor Jory ( Papillon, Gone With The Wind), stars as a ranch foreman wrongly arrested for murder. The memorable cast includes Tom Tyler (Stage Coach, Adventures of Captain Marvel), plus Noah Beery Jr (The Rockford Files) and in one of his earliest feature roles, Alan Ladd (The Blue Dahlia, Shane).

programme.title: Gunsmoke Ranch
programme.desc: Flagg is relocating flood victims to Gunsmoke Ranch. The Three Mesquiteers know Flagg to be a crook and try to warn them. They ignore the warning and improve the land only to find that it has been condemned for a new dam.

programme.title: Law of the Pampas
programme.desc: Murder below the Equator...and Hopalong Cassidy races to action in the heart of the wild Pampas country !Hoppy (William Boyd) and his pal Lucky (Russell Hayden) head to South America to look after a herd of cattle sold by Cassidys boss to an Argentine rancher. Unfortunately, the scoundrel Ralph Merritt (Sidney Blackmer) wants the cattle, and hes not above hiring some dangerous characters to do his dirty work. Its a test of blazing guns...under a blazing sun! Can the boys of Bar 20 lay down the law in a lawless place like the Pampas? Can Hoppy and his gang succeed in what is truly a last frontier? Watch and see!

programme.title: A Lust to Kill
programme.desc: An imprisoned outlaw escapes and goes on the hunt for his brothers murderers, who just happen to be members of the outlaws own gang. He and his beloved hit the trail, but are pursued by local law enforcement, who have their own plans for justice. Starring Don Megowan, Jim Davis, and Allison Hayes.

programme.title: Fighting Fury
programme.desc: A THRILLING TALE OF REVENGE AND REDEMPTION! Based on the story Triple Cross for Danger by the widely lauded Western author Walter J. Coburn, Fighting Fury is a thrilling take on the Western revenge drama. Portraying both a father and his son, star of silent and sound cowboy adventure films, Jack Hoxie (Trouble Busters, Law and Lawless) exudes the classic American rustic charm that still defines the genre. The film spins the yarn of Clay Hill Jr. (Hoxie), a Spanish-American boy raised by a Mexican servant who vows bloody vengeance on three malicious ranchers after they murder his parents and turn his life upside down. Featuring fine supporting performances from genre heavies Helen Holmes,...

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney take time out from their duties to try and collect the bounty posted on a legendary golden wolf that roams the Colorado foothills. A couple of wolf hunters dont take kindly to a pair of amateur hunters horning in on their range and attempt to drive the G-Men away before they can capture or kill their quarry.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men

Someone is tipping off Jackson as to the cattles whereabouts and when Roy learns who it is he has a plan to trap Jackson and clear his partner. Starring Roy Rogers, Lynne Roberts, and Myrtle Wiseman as Lulu Belle. Directed by Joseph Kane.

programme.desc: Roy Rogers, Gabby Hayes, and Smiley Burnette team up to protect the ranchers of Cherokee City from the false charges of illegal cattle trafficking. It may seem like the odds are against Roy, but just watch as he changes the course of the law with his flaming bullets, and, of course, a few songs. For trivia buffs: Smiley Burnette joined Roy because Gene Autry, the actor for whom he usually served as a sidekick, had joined the service!

programme.title: Daniel Boone
programme.desc: In 1775, Daniel Boone (George OBrien) leads thirty colonial families to Kentucky where they face the threats of Native American marauders led by rebel Simon Girty (John Carradine). Thats just the beginning, for there are even more dangers and clashes ahead for Boone and his party. With a cast that includes Ralph Forbes, Heather Angel, and lovable child star Dickie Jones, director David Howard takes us through one of the most exciting periods in American history!

programme.title: The Hanged Man
programme.desc: After a condemned gunfighter (Steve Forrest) survives his own hanging, he helps a young widow stop a pitiless land baron from taking her ranch. This television feature boasts a strong cast of recognizable characters, including Will Geer, Sharon Acker, Dean Jagger, BarBara Luna, and Cameron Mitchell. Director Michael Caffey would go on to work on such hit shows as Barnaby Jones and MacGyver. Also, look for John Mitchum, younger brother of Robert, in a small role. This movie originally aired on ABC-TV and was considered the pilot for a possible series. Writer/producer Andrew Fenady was behind several opular TV shows such as Branded and The Rebel, as well as the 1970 John Wayne feature, Chisum.

programme.title: Riders of Destiny
programme.desc: John Wayne sings! Well, not really. His voice was dubbed here, but as Singin Sandy Saunders hes still able to write the code of justice with a blazing sixgun! Hes a government agent out to help a group of ranchers in their battle with a villain who is tying up local water rights. Also starring Gabby Hayes, Al St. John, Yakima Canutt, and Cecilia Parker, Riders of Destiny was filmed early in Waynes career it was his first for Lone Star but the unmistakable swagger is already in place!

programme.title: Doomed Caravan
programme.desc: Hoppy is enlisted to help protect Jane Travers next caravan against robbers who have been terrorizing travelers. He comes across a wily pair of thieves who hve their men disguised as soldiers to escort the caravan. Hoppy isnt fooled for a second and busts up their plan with help from the Bar 20 boys. Not to be outdone, the thieves then capture everyone but Hoppy and puts them before a firing squad. Not its up to Hoppy to rescue his friends singlehandedly. The cast includes William Boyd as Hopalong Cassidy, with Russell Hayden and Andy Clyde as Luky Jenkins and California Jack. For those counting, this was the 32nd of 66 Hopalong Cassidy adventures. They would be edited for syndication...

programme.title: Ariel
programme.desc: Taisto jobbar i en gruva i norra Finland. Nar gruvan stangs reser han mot Helsingfors i en vrakig cabriolet som han ovantat får. Men problemen tornar upp sig. Han blir rånad, hittar inget jobb och doms till fangelse for misshandel. Men med hjalp av sin flickvan Irmeli, en ensamstående mor han traffar i Helsingfors och sin cellkamrat planerar Taisto att bryta sig ur fangelset och starta om på nytt. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Låt de doda vila
programme.desc: Jimmy ar inte bara en fan av heavy metal, skrack, och det ockulta. Han har ett mål: han vill kontakta sin avlidna mamma. Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: Vinski och osynlighetspulvret
programme.desc: Vinski och osynlighetspulvret utspelas i den fiktiva staden Hompstad, som skakas av en brottsvåg. Inbrott och rån har blivit en del av stadsbornas vardag och det behovs en riktig superhjalte for att hjalpa polisen. Skolpojken Vinski (Kuura Rossi) lar kanna den mystiske apotekaren (Martti Suosalo), som erbjuder Vinski mojligheten att bli Hompstads hjalte. Apotekarens hemlighet ar ett pulver, som gor personen osynlig och ger mojlighet att gå genom vaggar. Med hjalp av osynlighetspulvret skulle Vinski kunna avsloja en hemlig rånarliga och dess ledare, med endast ett par gula handskar som ledtråd.

programme.title: Skuggor i paradiset
programme.desc: Nikander ar en ensam sopbils-chauffor som en dag moter den anspråkslosa snabbkopskassorskan Ilona. Nikander blir blixtrande kar, men deras omsesidiga blyghet medfor att det romantiska lyser med sin frånvaro. Så plotsligt andras livet… Ilona får sparken och de bestammer sig for att traffas på ett mysigt litet motell. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin raknar dagarna till studenten då hon antligen får lamna småstaden och sin manipulativa syster for sina drommars New York. Allt ar perfekt och lokaltidningen på orten har lovat att publicera Kristins kronikor om staden som aldrig sover. Men Kristin missar planet och gommer sig istallet hemma hos Andrea, en marklig ung tjej, långt ute på landet for att undvika total fornedring. I huset ingenstans tar Kristin med Andrea till New Yorks pulserande hjarta i ett vindlande virtuellt aventyr som alla darhemma kan folja i hennes artiklar. Men så tranger sig verkligheten på.

programme.title: Svalan, Katten, Rosen, Doden
programme.desc: Munster upptacker kroppen av en ung strypt kvinna i hennes hem och overraskar mordaren som fortfarande finns i lokalen. Mordaren hinner fly men lamnar efter sig en sallsynt bok på platsen. Boken innehåller en halsning från den skyldige. Nar ett offer till hittas satts Van Veeterens litterara kunskaper på prov for att hinna stoppa seriemordaren innan fler mord begås.

programme.title: Klanen - berattelsen om Grudornas slakt
programme.desc: "Klanen" ar historien om en brottslig slakt dar Mika Kaurismaki behandlar existensens villkor genom den traditionella episka formen, på gransen mellan ratt och fel i lagen. Alexander, den yngsta sonen, ar slaktens vita får. Han forvantas hålla sig på den raka vagen, till skillnad från sin far och andra man i slakten. Men familjen ar varst, och blod ar tjockare an vatten... Familjedramat "Klanen" ar en storslagen hyllning till den gamla finska filmen.

programme.title: Leningrad Cowboys meet Moses
programme.desc: Film om varldens samsta rockgrupps hemfard från Mexiko till Sibirien. S: Matti Pellonpaa, Kari Vaananen, Andre Wilms och Leningrad Cowboys.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Juha
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis stumfilm efter Juhani Ahos triangeldrama hedrar oskuldens år i filmhistorien. Uttryckskraften i de svartvita bilderna stods av Anssi Tikanmakis musik.

programme.title: Fungi
programme.desc: En svamporganism har slagit ut storre delen av jordens befolkning. I en bunker någonstans i Sverige har ett forskarteam isolerat sig och kampar for att hitta ett botemedel. 19-åriga Leah forsoker anpassa sig till denna instangda tillvaro med sin pappa, militaren Gustav. Forskarduon Vera och Kim ser hoppet om en battre framtid hotas nar bunkerns ventilationssystem går sonder. Teamet tvingas ut på en farlig resa och det visar sig snart att svamporganismen inte ar det enda livsfarliga hotet i varlden utanfor.

programme.title: Lognaren
programme.desc: Lognaren ar en beskrivning av en ung skojare som aldrig talar sanning. Den unge mannen spelad av Aki Kaurismaki vandrar genom Helsingfors gator och forsoker låna pengar från bekanta och framlingar med olika forevandningar. Lognaren ar Mika Kaurismakis debutfilm och hans examensarbete från Munchens filmskola.

programme.title: Layers of Lies
programme.desc: Nar han återvander till Iran efter många år i exil i Finland, finner Sam (Ramin Sohrab) att han annu inte har flytt från sitt forflutna. En skum figur kidnappar hans fru Emma (Jessica Wolff) for att dra in honom i ett våldsamt plan for hamnd. Men Sam ar en obeveklig kampmaskin som inte kommer att stoppa någonting for att radda kvinnan han alskar. Nar det galler att bestamma sin framtid kommer det forflutna inte att stå i vagen for dem... Layer of Lies ar en adrenalinfylld spanningstur genom den livliga, mångsidiga metropolen Teheran.

programme.title: Calamari Union
programme.desc: Sjutton unga man, varav sexton heter Frank och bar svarta glasogon, lamnar en elandig arbetarmiljo och beger sig ut på en farlig resa genom storstaden på jakt efter den mytiska stadsdelen Eira. På grund av olika omstandigheter kommer bara två av dem fram. Men Eira ar inte riktigt det de hoppats på och deras sokande fortsatter – nu i en roddbåt mot Estland… Denna surrealistiska komedi ar Kaurismakis andra långfilm. En skon och absurd berattelse som blandar amerikansk gangsterfilm med finsk punk.

programme.title: Alena
programme.desc: Alenas (Amalia Holm) liv ar långt ifrån enkelt och det blir inte battre nar hon borjar på internatskolan Ekensberg, dar hennes liv utvecklas till ett rent helvete. Hon blir direkt trakasserad av de snobbiga tjejerna från lacrosselaget med gangledaren Filippa (Molly Nutley) i spetsen. Alenas basta van, Josefin (Felice Jankell), vagrar dock låta henne ta mer skit och om inte Alena gor något åt saken så kommer Josefin att rycka in, något som kan få odesdigra konsekvenser for alla… Alena ar en ”Låt den ratte komma in” moter ”Fucking Åmål” på Lundsberg.

programme.title: Fallet G
programme.desc: Van Veeterens enda olosta fall kommer upp till ytan igen nar dottern till en privatdetektiv kommer och besoker honom. En våldsam hustrumordare som forsvann under jord for flera år sedan verkar nu ha dykt upp med nytt namn och ar inblandad i ett nytt mord. Van Veeteren har såval professionella som personliga skal att satta fast honom.

programme.title: Ariel
programme.desc: Taisto jobbar i en gruva i norra Finland. Nar gruvan stangs reser han mot Helsingfors i en vrakig cabriolet som han ovantat får. Men problemen tornar upp sig. Han blir rånad, hittar inget jobb och doms till fangelse for misshandel. Men med hjalp av sin flickvan Irmeli, en ensamstående mor han traffar i Helsingfors och sin cellkamrat planerar Taisto att bryta sig ur fangelset och starta om på nytt. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Svalan, Katten, Rosen, Doden
programme.desc: Munster upptacker kroppen av en ung strypt kvinna i hennes hem och overraskar mordaren som fortfarande finns i lokalen. Mordaren hinner fly men lamnar efter sig en sallsynt bok på platsen. Boken innehåller en halsning från den skyldige. Nar ett offer till hittas satts Van Veeterens litterara kunskaper på prov for att hinna stoppa seriemordaren innan fler mord begås.

programme.title: Juha
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis stumfilm efter Juhani Ahos triangeldrama hedrar oskuldens år i filmhistorien. Uttryckskraften i de svartvita bilderna stods av Anssi Tikanmakis musik.

programme.title: Lognaren
programme.desc: Lognaren ar en beskrivning av en ung skojare som aldrig talar sanning. Den unge mannen spelad av Aki Kaurismaki vandrar genom Helsingfors gator och forsoker låna pengar från bekanta och framlingar med olika forevandningar. Lognaren ar Mika Kaurismakis debutfilm och hans examensarbete från Munchens filmskola.

programme.title: Tusen timmar
programme.desc: Svensk-danska filmen Tusen timmar handlar om Anna. Hon lever på drommar och soker karleken och sig sjalv. Hon har ett band med Thomas och de ar bara vanner, brukar de saga.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Mannen utan minne
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om en man som tappar sitt minne och får hjalp av fattiga men storhjartade manniskor i en containerby.

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: De arvlosa
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaens forsta långfilm. Han skrev manuset tillsammans med sin bror Aki. "De arvlosa" ar en tidlos skildring av hur småskurken Manne, bonddrangen Harri och den vackra Veera kor en Volga genom de forsvinnande finlandska landskapen, med poliser och gangsters standigt på halarna. Den fartfyllda resan ackompanjeras av tidlosa låtar av bland annat Juice och Rauli Badding.

programme.title: Vinski och osynlighetspulvret
programme.desc: Vinski och osynlighetspulvret utspelas i den fiktiva staden Hompstad, som skakas av en brottsvåg. Inbrott och rån har blivit en del av stadsbornas vardag och det behovs en riktig superhjalte for att hjalpa polisen. Skolpojken Vinski (Kuura Rossi) lar kanna den mystiske apotekaren (Martti Suosalo), som erbjuder Vinski mojligheten att bli Hompstads hjalte. Apotekarens hemlighet ar ett pulver, som gor personen osynlig och ger mojlighet att gå genom vaggar. Med hjalp av osynlighetspulvret skulle Vinski kunna avsloja en hemlig rånarliga och dess ledare, med endast ett par gula handskar som ledtråd.

programme.title: Total Balalaika Show
programme.desc: Total Balalaika Show ar en dokumentar om en otrolig handelse, ett fantastiskt mote mellan ost och vast. I juni 1993 genomfordes en historisk konsert i Helsingfors. Rockgruppen Leningrad Cowboys spelade tillsammans med Alexandrov Ensemblen (Roda Armen) , en kor med 100 sångare, ca 40 musiker och 20 dansare. Tillsammans framforde de bland annat ”Happy Together”, ”Delilah”, ”Gimme All Your Lovin’” och ”Knocking On Heaven’s Door”. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Papperstjarnan
programme.desc: "Pappersstjarnan" ar baserad på verkliga handelser. Det handlar om en fotomodell, hennes tre man, ett dekadent liv, utnyttjande och offentlig kritik. Anna (Pirkko Hamalainen) ar en fore detta miss, nu en toppmodell, vars liv spårar ur på grund av mannen. Anna blir så småningom foremål for utnyttjande av både den skumma affarsmannen Ulf (Hannu Lauri) och den alkoholiserade och våldsamma fotografen Ilja (Kari Vaananen). Den enda riktiga vannen visar sig vara Taukka (Matti Rasila), som har en modig installning till livet. Anna beslutar sig for att forsoka fly från de svåra delarna av sitt liv, men det kraver modiga beslut och beredskap att betala deras pris.

programme.title: Layers of Lies
programme.desc: Nar han återvander till Iran efter många år i exil i Finland, finner Sam (Ramin Sohrab) att han annu inte har flytt från sitt forflutna. En skum figur kidnappar hans fru Emma (Jessica Wolff) for att dra in honom i ett våldsamt plan for hamnd. Men Sam ar en obeveklig kampmaskin som inte kommer att stoppa någonting for att radda kvinnan han alskar. Nar det galler att bestamma sin framtid kommer det forflutna inte att stå i vagen for dem... Layer of Lies ar en adrenalinfylld spanningstur genom den livliga, mångsidiga metropolen Teheran.

programme.title: Bieffekterna
programme.desc: Forskarstudenten Julia och programmeraren Rebecca ingår i ett elitteam vid Lunds universitet. De jobbar med den kontroversiella vetenskapliga metoden biohacking, genteknikens nya hopp som kan betyda slutet for dodliga sjukdomar i vår livstid.

programme.title: Calamari Union
programme.desc: Sjutton unga man, varav sexton heter Frank och bar svarta glasogon, lamnar en elandig arbetarmiljo och beger sig ut på en farlig resa genom storstaden på jakt efter den mytiska stadsdelen Eira. På grund av olika omstandigheter kommer bara två av dem fram. Men Eira ar inte riktigt det de hoppats på och deras sokande fortsatter – nu i en roddbåt mot Estland… Denna surrealistiska komedi ar Kaurismakis andra långfilm. En skon och absurd berattelse som blandar amerikansk gangsterfilm med finsk punk.

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.desc: Peter narmar sig 30 och ar fortfarande vilsen svulsten efter karlek med andlosa online dater utan resultat. En nyckfull date lamnar honom ensam i sangen en morgon nar han vaknar. Peter forsoker lamna allt bakom sig och fortsatter med nya dater från samma site. For varje date oppnas en helt ny varld av upplevelser och erfarenheter som får honom att ifrågasatta allt med naturkrafter, attraktion och akta karlek. Den stora frågan forblir obesvarad, kan Peter verkligen bli foralskad och hitta den akta karleken?

programme.title: Loves Last Resort
programme.desc: Efter att ha dejtat i tio år har Chloes pojkvan Eric annu ite mognat till den man hon onskar han skulle vara. Hon hoppas skynda på forloppet genom att dumpa honom. Sex månader senare traffas de och Eric avslojar nyheten om att han ska gifta sig. For att komma bort tar hon semester och på samma semesterort dyker Eric med flickvan upp.

programme.title: The Right Kind of Wrong
programme.desc: Leo Palamino ar den misslyckade forfattaren som blev diskare som blev beromd for alla sina fel och brister genom bloggen “Varfor du suger”, den enorma natsuccen som skrivs av hans exfru. Leo traffar sen Colette, sin dromtjej … samma dag som hon gifter sig med den perfekte mannen. Det blir borjan på den ultimata underdog-historien nar den oradde drommaren Leo riskerar allt for att visa Colette och hela varlden allt som ar ratt med en man som ar kand for att inte ha ett enda ratt.

programme.title: You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger
programme.desc: I denna stormiga komedi av Woody Allen, upptacker två par att graset inte alltid ar gronare på andra sidan. Alfie Shepridge (ANTHONY HOPKINS) dumpar sin fru sedan 40 år (GEMMA JONES), i ett forsok att återuppleva ungdomens nojen tillsammans med en ung callgirl (LUCY PUNCH). For att få ratsida på sitt liv tar den forsmådda hustrun hjalp av en spådam. Samtidigt blir deras dotter Sally (NAOMI WATTS) foralskad i sin chef (ANTONIO BANDERAS), och hennes make (JOSH BROLIN) blir besatt av skonheten som bor på andra sidan gatan (FREIDA PINTO). Och snart hanger både deras forhållanden och deras forstånd i samma skora tråd...

programme.title: Leading Lady

I gentjanst arrangerar Jodi den årliga konserten på Willemses gård. Jodis upplevelser i Brandfort lar henne att det finns mer i livet an Hollywoods filmvarld... eller gor det det?

Driven av spontana och instinktiva handlingar foralskar sig Charlie i en mystisk, rumansk kvinna med ett morkt och våldsamt forflutet.

De gor upp en pakt om att forlora oskulden under den sista sommaren fore collegestudierna, men denna varma sommar satts deras vanskap for forsta gången på prov nar de råkar falla for en och samma kille. Han beter sig sjalviskt och allmant illa mot sina kollegor och sin 8-årige son Oscar, men aven mot de många kvinnorna i hans liv, exfrun Karen, kollegan Sally, psykologen Miriam, Lisa som ar lyckligt gift, prostituerade Lesley och maklaren Carol som skulle salja hans hus. Den omhetstorstande Marilyn kanner sig overgiven av maken Arthur Miller och attraherad av Oliviers assistent, den unge Colin Clark. Colin blir snart Marilyns fasta och trygga punkt, samtidigt som han också blir Oliviers endahopp att kunna slutfora sin film genom sin formåga att hålla den impulsiva Marilyn i schakt. Upp over oronen foralskadar det nu Colins hjarta som riskerar att krossas av varldens storsta och vackraste filmstjarna!

Han kanner sig vilse och overgiven, blir van med en grupp utlandska studenter och kastar sig in i utbytesstudenternas varld. Han tar sig utanfor sin egen bekvamlighetszon och forsoker få en nystart i livet, men bakom varje horn lurar en påminnelse om hans fore detta flickvan, och han kampar for att hitta ett avslut. Ett karleksbrev till Granada som blandar dokumentar med fiktion for att skapa en verklig och akta skildring av hur det går till att upptacka sig sjalv. Filmad i ett unikt bildforhållande som aldrig tidigare visats på bio.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E16 SCL 2014 Season 1, Episode 16, Malaysia (World Finals Part 2)

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: Across seven rivers, through mountains and forests, 12 strongmen go to toughest places to find out who is strongest Viking in the World and open a new season of Strongman champions league for 2015. Events like the Hercules Hold, Yoke Race and pulling a real Viking ship are some of the ingredients of this fantastic show.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: The second stage of Strongman champions league will be hosted in Germany, by FIBO - the leading international trade show for fitness, wellness and health worldwide with 300,000 visitors in four days. Special implements like the biggest log in the world or the special Bavarian stone lift are not only a challenge, but also an opportunity for new personal, national and world records.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 3, Holland
programme.desc: Holland is hosting 12 different countries with 14 of the strongest men in the world for the third stage of the Strongman Champions League.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 4, Finland
programme.desc: Zydrunas Savickas, one of strongest people on earth is in this competition which has attracted the attention of the audience in the battle for the title of strongest man in Finland. The next round of SCL is in Bulgaria.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 5, Bulgaria
programme.desc: The next stage of the competition is in Bulgaria where Ervin Katona (SCL World Champion 2012) will compete for the last time.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E06 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 6, Latvia
programme.desc: Krzysztof Radzikowski, the leader in the league will fight hard to keep Dainis Zageris off from the title and to gather another 25 ranking points in this next stage in Latvia.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E07 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 7, Croatia
programme.desc: The competition sees a close battle with a new world record in overhead dumbbell and close finishes throughout the day. This stage is in Croatia, in a city over 1700 years old, steeped in Roman tradition and history, the athletes arrive for the truck pull after a picturesque boat ride on the Adriatic Sea.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E08 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 8, Poland
programme.desc: We are now half way through the SCL 2015 and getting closer to the grand world finals in Turkey. The eighth stage is in Poland, the home country of the current leader Krzysztof Radzikowski.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E09 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 9, Austria
programme.desc: In this stage we go into the mountains of Austria to find out through six grueling events who is the strongest in the land of Alps. Martin Wildauer, current World Champion 2014 and Austrian local is competing alongside Zageris, Radzikowski, Belsak and many others.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E10 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 10, Romania
programme.desc: The 10th stage of this years competition in Strongman Champions League is held in the Romanian city of Sibiu where the 12 strongmen continue to compete for the title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E11 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 11, World Log Lift Championship
programme.desc: The 11th stage is the SCL Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. In this championship, each competitor must lift three different weights overhead. Zydrunas Savickas is the current world record holder in the Log Lift.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E12 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 12, Lithuania
programme.desc: This next episode of the Strongman Champions League is hosted in Lithuania and sees us getting one step closer to the final.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E13 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 13, Portugal
programme.desc: The 13th stage of Strongman Champions League is in Maia, Portugal. The competition is at the “Powerexpo” – one of the best sport and fitness events in Portugal.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E14 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 14, Martinique
programme.desc: This stage is in Martinique and eight strongmen from all over the world will compete for the last chance to gather points before the world grand finals in December.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E15 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 15, Lightweight World Championship
programme.desc: A special World championship under the newcomers and lightweights in the Strongman world. Some of them will step from this to the heavyweights divisions.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E16 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 16, World Finals Turkey
programme.desc: After 15 outstanding competitions all over the world, finally we are here at the final competition of this year’s Strongman Champions League hosted in Turkey.

programme.desc: Laura Compagni teams up with Mataj Architects and The Parentela Family to introduce the first of the Hotel Vie chain of luxury hotels.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: It is time to upsize! Daryls client is moving away from downtown Toronto because they desire a bigger space, more privacy, and tranquility. They have 3 children between the ages of 7 and 13 who need their own bedrooms and the lady of the house needs an office since she works from home. Daryl knows all about tranquility and goes golfing with Mike to discuss his client and Mikes listing for them.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Mikes couple is looking for their luxurious dream home anywhere in between Toronto and Barrie near HWY 400 in a prestigious neighborhood. They have a large dog, tall family, and want to start a family of their own. This means they are going to need a lot of space and want the house to be fully renovated or brand-new. Mike is the perfect agent for this couple because he lives, eats, and breathes the luxury lifestyle.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: An amazing beachfront property is what Inezs couple is looking for and these top million dollar agents are sure to surpass their expectations. Inezs client currently lives in a condo and have one child, however, they desire a home that they can comfortably expand their family in.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Mikes friend invites him to an Indian wedding and tells him about his uncle who is looking for a luxury condo close to the airport. Daryl, Inez, and Jin support and donate to Mikes charity after winning a bet amongst them and the amount is determined by how long Mike lasts in the ring boxing against a professional. This client is looking for an investment property and a place for him to live when visiting.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: A young trendy couple wants to start a family in Toronto but they need some help from these top million dollar agents. Jin is a natural daredevil and has always wanted to skydive with her clients. In Oakville, Jin practices at iFly that is an indoor skydiving facility. Jins client lives a very active and busy lifestyle so they require somewhere with low maintenance but still has enough space for a big family. Inez takes Jin to her hair stylist Anastasia for some business and pleasure.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Moving in together can be stressful but fun because you are starting a new life together! Inezs client is selling their separate properties and looking for a house or condo in the city or beach area that is close to shopping, groceries, schools, etc. Inezs couple is not too picky and open to different kinds of properties. Daryl and Inez enjoy a beautiful bike ride along the beaches boardwalk to discuss her client and the perfect luxury listing he has found.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Agreeing on a vacation home is made much harder when these top million dollar agents have astounding listings. Mikes client is looking for a waterfront cottage with lots of land and privacy. What better way to check out some waterfront listings then from a helicopter? Debbie wants a family cottage that feels homey, however, Paul wants an impressive high-end cottage that he can bring his business clients to.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Now that Kristen and Kane have opened an office in Toronto, they will be travelling a lot from Vancouver and want somewhere of their own to stay in. Daryl and the other top million dollar agents have a wide range to search over because Daryls client is willing to live an hour or two drive away from downtown Toronto. Daryl, Jin, and Mike meet up for lunch in Port Dover to discuss business and later in the episode Mike and Daryl get their hands dirty in the kitchen at Sababa Restaurant.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Many people enjoy staying busy and always having a project on the go. Inezs client loves to build and create breathtaking properties. On their next project, this couple wants an interesting property, preferably waterfront, which they can use for an investment property or to build on. Inez takes her client on a private yacht so they can cruise around Lake Ontario and discuss the clients wish list.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E13 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Deborah and Vezi are an international couple that want to live in Toronto for one year but has no idea where to start looking. Luckily for them Mike, Jin, Daryl, and Inez have teamed up to find them the home of their dreams. They agree to split the commission and throw a yacht party for the clients decision. Mike arranges a private plane for all four agents to go to Montreal and discuss in style what the client is looking for.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: The King is back, baby! Daryl King is known to make an entrance, and he wants the houses he shows to have that same "wow" factor. His clients are looking for a grand mansion, and with their sizeable budget wont settle for anything less than spectacular.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: International luxury realtor Mike Donia jets off to Thailand to work with a client and good friend of his, Mae. She is moving back to her hometown of Bangkok to pursue her modeling career, and is looking for the house of her dreams. Mike has his work cut out for him, as Maes long wish list will be hard to achieve with her budget.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: With the help of a Bangkok real estate expert, Max Gloeckner, Mike is confident he can deliver just what Mae is looking for. This episode features the last two of four properties, as well as the reveal of which house the client decides to purchase.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Vicky is searching for a home in The Beaches for her and her family. No one knows the Beach like Inez Kudryk, so Vicky enlists her help in finding some stunning luxury properties to tour. With a grand budget and very particular tastes, Inez knows that Vicky will be a tough client to please.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E07 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Steve Bailey to save the day! This weeks episode features the lovely couple Chris and Rosa as they search for the perfect home. While Rosa is mainly concerned with cutting down her commute, Chris just wants to feel a connection to a property. Luckily for Steve, hes got his sister Helen, an interior designer and home stager, to help sway Chris - and it works!

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Unfortunately for Rosa, she isnt seeing the benefits of moving to a town around Cambridge. Steves got some neat ideas, but will they be able to convince Rosa? This episode features the last two of four properties, as well as the reveal of which house the clients decide to purchase.

programme.title: Childs Play (2019)
programme.desc: Från producenterna bakom ”DET” kommer CHILD’S PLAY, en helt ny version av den klassiska skrackberattelsen om den onda dockan Chucky, nu med Mark Hamill som gor rosten. Nar Karen koper den hogteknologiska Buddi-dockan till sin son Andy i fodelsedagspresent bjuder hon omedvetet in ondska i sitt hem. Nu galler det bara for Andy att få de vuxna att lyssna, så att de kan stoppa dockan innan det ar for sent.

programme.title: Suicide Kings
programme.desc: Avery ar desperat: hans syster ar kidnappad och losensumman ar 2 miljoner dollar, och hans pappa har inte pengarna. Så Avery och hans polare kokar ihop en tuff, halvt sjalvmordsbenagen plan: att rova bort den pensionerade maffiabossen Charlie Bartolucci och tvinga honom att hitta flickan.

programme.title: Legacy of lies
programme.desc: Scott Adkins spelar den hårde dorrvakten Martin Baxter som drygar ut inkomsterna genom att stalla upp i måttligt lagliga kampsportstavlingar. I bakgrunden finns en karriar som MI6-agent han lamnade efter ett uppdrag i Kiev som slutade med katastrof. Men det forflutna har ju en tendens att hinna ikapp folk inom hans profession. Nar Baxter får chansen att grava fram vad det egentligen var som hande den dar odesdigra kvallen i Kiev tar han den.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Rosso
programme.desc: Rosso, som skickligt kombinerar roadmovie och kriminaldrama, ar berattelsen om den sicilianska lonnmordaren Giancarlo Rosso, som har kommit till Finland for att leta efter sitt nasta mål, som råkar vara hans alskade Marja. Ovantat får Rosso hjalp med spårningen av Marjas bror Martti, trots att de inte ens delar ett gemensamt språk. På resan ingår både skrotningsuppdrag och några rån...

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: De arvlosa
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaens forsta långfilm. Han skrev manuset tillsammans med sin bror Aki. "De arvlosa" ar en tidlos skildring av hur småskurken Manne, bonddrangen Harri och den vackra Veera kor en Volga genom de forsvinnande finlandska landskapen, med poliser och gangsters standigt på halarna. Den fartfyllda resan ackompanjeras av tidlosa låtar av bland annat Juice och Rauli Badding.

programme.title: My Week With Marilyn
programme.desc: I ett desperat forsok att bli tagen på storre allvar reser ikonen Marilyn Monroe (Michelle Williams) till London 1956 for att spela mot legenden Laurence Olivier i “Prinsen och balettflickan”. Den omhetstorstande Marilyn kanner sig overgiven av maken Arthur Miller och attraherad av Oliviers assistent, den unge Colin Clark. Colin blir snart Marilyns fasta och trygga punkt, samtidigt som han också blir Oliviers endahopp att kunna slutfora sin film genom sin formåga att hålla den impulsiva Marilyn i schakt. Upp over oronen foralskadar det nu Colins hjarta som riskerar att krossas av varldens storsta och vackraste filmstjarna!

programme.title: The Dresser
programme.desc: En odesdiger natt på en liten engelsk teater under andra varldskriget, satter en trupp med kringresande skådespelare upp Shakespeares "King Lear".

programme.title: Underligare an fiktion
programme.desc: En IRS-revisor finner sig plotsligt foremål for berattande som bara han kan hora: berattande som borjar påverka hela hans liv; från hans arbete; till hans karleksintresse; till sin dod.

programme.title: Death At A Funeral
programme.desc: En komisk vriden historia om en dysfunktionell familj som samlas for att sorja sin patriarks bortgång. Daniels far har just avlidit och det enda han vill ar att genomfora begravningen som planerat, vilket inte ar det lattaste med en galen familj på halsen. Brorsan ar mest intresserad av att ragga tjejer, en annan slakting ar overtygad om att fadern ar vid liv i kistan och en mystisk pillerburk dyker standigt upp. Denna dråpliga komedi i brittisk tradition bjuder på många overraskningar.

programme.title: 10 Items or Less
programme.desc: Oscar och Golden Globevinnaren Morgan Freeman spelar har en filmstjarna som ger sig ut på rollforberedande research i ett snabbkop i ostra Los Angeles. Han moter en snabbtalande kassorska (Paz Vega) och de ger sig av på en gemensam resa for att visa varandra sina respektive varldar. Strandad utan vare sig mobiltelefon eller bil accepterar han tjejens erbjudande om att ge honom lift tillbaka till Beverly Hills. Under resans gång upptacker emellertid det har till synes omaka paret att de har vissa gemensamma namnare som for all framtid kommer att forandra deras syn på deras egna liv...

programme.title: My Old Lady
programme.desc: Den utfattige New York-bon Mathias arver en lagenhet i Paris av sin far som han inte haft någon kontakt med. Nar han anlander till staden finner han till sin forvåning att en aldre, sofistikerad dam, Mathilde, och hennes mycket beskyddande dotter bor i våningen. Enligt en uråldrig fransk lag kan han inte krava tilltrade till egendomen forran Mathilde dott. Mathias bestammer sig andå for att forsoka salja lagenheten samtidigt som det visar sig att hans far och Mathilde lange burit på en hemlighet.

programme.title: Don Jon
programme.desc: Don Martell ar en kille från New Jersey, vars liv kretsar kring familjen, vannerna, kyrkan – och porr. Formågan att ragga upp nya tjejer varje helg har gett honom smeknamnet ”Don Jon”. En kvall traffar han den snygga och romantiska Barbara som letar efter en underbar dromkille, en idealbild som ar valdigt långt från Don.

programme.title: Plan A
programme.desc: Filmen ar baserad på en sann historia. Forintelseoverlevaren och juden Max moter i Tyskland 1945 en grupp radikala judiska motståndskampar som precis som han har forlorat allt framtidshopp efter att de har berovats sina liv och efter att alla deras nara och kara har mordats av nazisterna. De drommer om vedergallning i episk skala for det judiska folket. Filmen handlar om deras livsfarliga och djarva hemliga operation som kallades Plan A.

programme.title: The Blair Witch Project
programme.desc: THE BLAIR WITCH PROJECT foljer en trio filmskapare på vad som borde ha varit en enkel promenad i skogen men blir snabbt en utflykt till hjartstoppande terror. Nar de tre oforklarligt går forlorade forsamras moral. Hunger borjar. Anklagelser flyger. Nar slutet av resan narmar sig inser de att det de filmar nu inte ar en legend ... utan deras egen nedstigning till otankbar skrack.

programme.title: Bedragaren
programme.desc: Den 60-åriga miljardaren Robert Miller framstår som en framgångsrik man, både i arbetslivet och privat. Men i verkligheten ar han i desperat behov av att avsluta forsaljningen av sitt imperium till en stor bank innan hans stora bedrageri avslojas. Miller jobbar hårt for att uppratthålla fasaden infor sin fru, dotter, affarspartner och den franska alskarinnan. Men precis då allt verkar falla på plats blir Robert inblandad i en bilolycka som han smiter från. Polismannen Michael Bryer fattar misstankar mot Robert och den annars så kompromisslosa affarsmannen måste nu konfrontera granserna for sin egen dubbelmoral.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Cypher
programme.desc: I ett skuggigt rike av foretagsspionage, snubblar en uttråkad alla in i ett nat av bedrageri och blir en omedveten spion. Nar han navigerar i forraderi och svek, samarbetar han med en forforisk gåta for att avsloja chockerande sanningar och återta sin identitet.

programme.title: Instrument of War
programme.desc: Den amerikanska piloten Clair Cline blir nedskjuten och hamnar i fångenskap i norra Tyskland. En kamp tar slut, en annan tar vid – att hålla hoppet vid liv trots taggtråd och fortryck. Cline och hans medfångar måste hitta ett satt att hålla ihop, inte bara for att overleva utan aven for att utharda fångenskapen. Baserad på sanna handelser.

programme.title: Hope Springs
programme.desc: Efter 30 års aktenskap; ett medelålders par deltar i en intensiv veckolång rådgivningssession for att jobba på deras forhållande.

programme.title: What We Did On Our Holiday
programme.desc: Doug (David Tennant) och Abi (Rosamund Pike) ar två helt vanliga foraldrar med tre charmiga men valdigt excentriska barn. Nar det hårda foraldralivet hotar deras mentala halsa och aktenskap så bestammer de sig for att ta med barnen på en resa till Skottland till ett stort slaktkalas och for att halsa på Dougs minst sagt knappa pappa Gordie (Billy Connolly). Det som skulle bli en forsoningsresa forvandlas snabbt till ett hysteriskt roligt socialt katastrofområde nar osamja,

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Hollywoods hemlighet
programme.desc: 1924 samlade mediamogulen William Randolph Hearst några av varldens mest kanda personligheter for en resa med sin yacht som resulterade i ett mord som forblev olost.

programme.title: My Old Lady
programme.desc: Den utfattige New York-bon Mathias arver en lagenhet i Paris av sin far som han inte haft någon kontakt med. Nar han anlander till staden finner han till sin forvåning att en aldre, sofistikerad dam, Mathilde, och hennes mycket beskyddande dotter bor i våningen. Enligt en uråldrig fransk lag kan han inte krava tilltrade till egendomen forran Mathilde dott. Mathias bestammer sig andå for att forsoka salja lagenheten samtidigt som det visar sig att hans far och Mathilde lange burit på en hemlighet.

programme.title: 200 Cigarettes
programme.desc: Det ar nyårsafton i New York, år 1981. Monica ska ha fest, men vid niotiden har ingen dykt upp. Hennes gaster ar på vag, men de har inte bråttom. Kevin har ingen lust att fira nyår eftersom han nyligen blivit dumpad. Val och Stephie går vilse och hamnar på en klubb. Bridget och Caitlyn forsoker bli av med Bridgets pojkvan Eric. Alla ar de på jakt efter sex, karlek eller båda två.

programme.title: Staden Ember
programme.desc: Det har gått 200 år sedan den sista manniskan sokte skydd i den underjordiska staden Ember; men nu sviktar den stora generatorn.

programme.title: Arlington Road
programme.desc: I denna tata thriller moter vi collegeprofessorn Michael Faraday vars fru, en FBI-agent, dodats av medlemmar av en hogerextrem terroristgrupp. Nar Michael blir van med sina nya grannar, Oliver och Cheryl Lang, får han snart anledning att misstanka att något inte står ratt till. Han borjar forska i deras forflutna, men inte utan risk for sitt liv.

programme.title: Suicide Kings
programme.desc: Avery ar desperat: hans syster ar kidnappad och losensumman ar 2 miljoner dollar, och hans pappa har inte pengarna. Så Avery och hans polare kokar ihop en tuff, halvt sjalvmordsbenagen plan: att rova bort den pensionerade maffiabossen Charlie Bartolucci och tvinga honom att hitta flickan.

programme.title: Suburra
programme.desc: Efter att en underårig prostituerad overdoserar på droger fastnar en korrupt politiker i handerna på en skoningslos maffiaboss som kallar sig Samurai. Han vill utnyttja politikerns position for att utveckla Roms hamn till en ny Las Vegas. Detta blir startskottet for en vild historia som letar sig från Roms gator fram till parlamentet och anda in till Vatikanen.

programme.title: World Heritage
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 World Heritage Ancient Temples of Egypt, Egypt (ENG)
programme.desc: Explore the ancient heritage sites of Abu Simbel, the Philae complex of Nubia and the Hatshepsut Temple to unravel the mystical stories behind the ancient temples of Egypt.

programme.title: 10 Days Scotland
programme.desc: Robbie’s adventures in Perth kick off with him immersing himself in the historic grandeur of the Scone Castle, where a mysterious stone tells tales of Scottish monarchs. But the real thunder of the Highlands awaits at the Braemar Games gathering, where tartan meets brawn, and Robbie learns that embracing his Scottish side involves more than just kilts and castles.

programme.title: Backpack Serbia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E27 Backpack Novi Sad, Serbia
programme.desc: Heather explores Novi Sad, the financial and industrial hub of Serbia.Starting with canoeing on Danube and later exploring the city and its landmarks.

programme.title: Boarding Pass
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Boarding Pass Santa Village, Finland
programme.desc: Emeline Nsingi Nkosi goes to Santa Village at Rovaniemi, where she reads some of the letters that children from around the world write to him.

programme.title: Xplore Bulgaria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Xplore Bulgaria Sunny Beach
programme.desc: Luxurious hotels, thrilling water parks, inexpensive food and almost 300 days of bright sunny weather make Bulgaria’s biggest seaside resort, Sunny Beach popular for budget beach getaways. programme.title: USA: The end of oil - Part 2

programme.desc: "The end of oil" is the amazing story of a raw material which has revolutionized mans life in just a century. But today, oil reserves are depleting. In his crazy race for always more production, Man didnt manage to preserve this precious energy that took million years for the Earth to give out. To tell the adventure of oil, Yann Arthus-Bertrand and his team went to the United States, the country which depends the most on black gold. At the start of the 21st century, it is now urgent to realize that oil resources are limited. Its today that we have to act and get organized, in order to prepare the new era to come. While all our economies are based on the petrol barrels price, well...

programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 4 - Nature’s Heroes: Senegal - Part 1
programme.desc: For this new episode, Yann Arthus-Bertrand travels through Senegal to encounter men and women who dedicate their lives to preserving the environment. One of the major ecological stakes of the country is fishing and the mangrove ecosystem which, like in some many other parts of the world, faces major threats. Yann Arthus-Bertrand presents the struggle of Haidar El Ali, chosen among one of the world’s most active ecologists. He creates protected marine areas and reforests the disappeared mangrove of his country. He’s managed to convince thousands of Senegalese to plant with him ten million mangrove trees.
